metadata.description:
Whox7 (print edition)  
26x36 inch including 1inch border  
Digital composition made with Blender and Cables.GL  
February 2023

This token comes with the physical print using the Artfora print-on-demand service. 

You can claim the print by using the website artfora.com. Please reach out to the artist at info@professor-wrecks.com with any questions.

If you are purchasing this token on the secondary market, check artfora.com first for the claim status: if it hasn't been claimed yet by its previous owner(s), you may still claim the drawing. But if it has already been claimed, you should communicate with the seller to arrange the shipping of the physical drawing. The artist is not responsible for any issues that may arise concerning a secondary sale.
